    "kernel": "6.1.10-200.fc37.x86_64",
    "notes": "The new EA App makes it impossible to set command line arguments to games that were bought on Steam. I also temporarily disabled my webcam with `sudo modprobe -r uvcvideo`, which was also one of the crash reasons, and now the game crashes after the Loading screen starts fading out. Previously it crashed before that.",
